given your abilities.

95
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,403
However...

96
00:06:12,220 --> 00:06:14,430
I can sense that the sign
is a bit peculiar.

97
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:16,367
Peculiar?

98
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:19,398
It seems to have been added
with something extra.

99
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:24,220
Now I will use the profound power
of wandering souls' destiny in this world

100
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:26,367
to discover its true shape.

101
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:28,421
What?

102
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:31,480
Wow, this is really something.

103
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:35,347
These strong lines do not appear
to be controlled by threads or magnets.

104
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:38,360
Compared to divination,

105
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:41,140
this arouses more interest
in me as a magician.

106
00:06:41,900 --> 00:06:43,276
The original sign

107
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:45,577
was missing a horizontal stroke.

108
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,171
This is my final divination result.

109
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,646
Gotcha!

110
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:55,860
I actually managed to find it.

111
00:06:56,658 --> 00:06:58,460
Wait a moment.

112
00:06:58,619 --> 00:07:00,320
If he is truly a member of
the mysterious organization,

113
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:02,831
