So let's stop here.

117
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:21,900
However, I also have my own principles.

118
00:07:22,980 --> 00:07:25,065
I cannot simply turn a blind eye

119
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,183
to this misdrawn sign.

120
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:32,420
However, unless I point out to Solitaire
personally, it has no significance.

121
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:34,520
CRITICAL HIT

122
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,813
Is that so?

123
00:07:36,140 --> 00:07:37,767
I will take it as a reference.

124
00:07:38,460 --> 00:07:40,200
Then I'll take my leave.

125
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:42,460
-Oh, there's one more thing.
-What is it?

126
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,461
Do you have an impression of

127
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:47,622
a girl sitting in a wheelchair
with braided hair?

128
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:52,940
I couldn't make out what she was saying.

129
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:55,485
But she seemed to show concern

130
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,503
about the path you were on.

131
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:01,535
Her spirit body actually took
the shape of a wheelchair.

132
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:04,451
This only happens if one spends
a lot of time in a wheelchair.

133
00:08:05,420 --> 00:08:07,380
But I can't talk to her anymore.

134
00:08:08,340 --> 00:08:11,300
It should be my guardian spirit
or something like that.

135
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,360
I will think about it

136
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:14,998
and come up with a solution.

137
00:08:20,140 --> 00:08:23,020
Then it appears that I do not need to
force her to ascend to heaven.

138
00:08:23,820 --> 00:08:26,540
You have succeeded in arousing
my interest, Diviner.

139
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,960
I thought he was just a fraud

140
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:31,240
who used hot reading to pretend
to have supernatural powers.

141
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:34,260
But how did he know about the kid?

142
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:38,083
What exactly did he see?

143
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:41,510
Wow, it really lives up to its reputation.

144
00:08:41,740 --> 00:08:43,380
He is adorable.

145
00:08:43,598 --> 00:08:45,920
You only pay attention to the appearance.

146
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,700
Ah, it's raining.

147
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:51,169
Oops, I didn't bring an umbrella.

148
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:54,000
Then let me lend you my umbrella.
I still have my raincoat.

149
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:57,092
If I get caught in the rain,
my disguise makeup will be ruined.

150
00:08:57,740 --> 00:09:01,244
I really admire the energy
of young people.

151
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,490
I see.

152
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:09,351
You seem to have noticed this
as much as I did.

153
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:14,820
However, it is a coincidence

154
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:18,760
that I was asked
the same question twice today.

155
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:22,183
But, speaking of which,

156
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:25,191
(EXERCISE CAUTION WITH FIRE)
I cannot stand the girl's

157
00:09:25,191 --> 00:09:27,531
(EXERCISE CAUTION WITH FIRE)
choice of raincoat.

158
00:09:28,224 --> 00:09:29,504
SAKURAMONDA STATION

159
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:36,157
We have dispatched
hundreds of investigators

160
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:39,400
to conduct road inspections

161
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:41,613
and retrieve surveillance footage

162
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:44,470
in order to pinpoint
Solitaire's movements.

163
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:47,800
However, we still do not know

164
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:50,160
what his ultimate objective is.

165
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:55,100
His current interest is…

166
00:09:55,552 --> 00:09:57,184
(TENA SORIMURA, SELF-PROCLAIMED MAGICIAN)

167
00:09:59,160 --> 00:10:00,536
