the snake out of its hole?

168
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:04,400
Only a very few people know about

169
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,760
the difference between
that sign and the original one.

170
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:10,720
But this matter cannot be
disclosed here, right?

171
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:14,435
Yes. We still don't know who the enemy is.

172
00:10:15,300 --> 00:10:17,927
Whoever made that person disappear without
a trace must be a formidable opponent.

173
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:22,211
If we casually drop the bait now, there's
a possibility of being counterattacked.

174
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:29,538
Although my primary job is to investigate
the whereabouts of Solitaire,

175
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:33,113
if I try to focus on more than one thing,
it will throw me off track.

176
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:36,934
Once Solitaire is captured, progress
will be made on all other matters.

177
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,809
And you should be pleased

178
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,360
that there are more people
available to be mobilized.

179
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,580
