180
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:45,620
while you sip your coffee.

181
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,119
Someone who once lagged
behind in his career

182
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:50,400
has unexpectedly made it to the top.

183
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:52,077
Thank you for your compliment.

184
00:10:52,310 --> 00:10:54,187
Thanks to your blessings,

185
00:10:54,187 --> 00:10:55,772
I now have at least the authority
to command you all.

186
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:59,870
Moreover, since you still have
the energy to complain to me,

187
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:02,563
it seems that you haven't reached
the level of being completely exhausted.

188
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:04,930
Don't get too carried away.

189
00:11:05,580 --> 00:11:09,959
You were Hosorogi's sidekick before this.
You had many detractors.

190
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:12,532
Oh, I see.

191
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,634
I thought that
those corrupt police officers

192
00:11:15,980 --> 00:11:17,711
who can no longer openly
engage in private misconduct

193
00:11:17,711 --> 00:11:20,005
would be the only ones to resent me
because of the internal review.

194
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:23,160
Be clear about your status

195
00:11:23,460 --> 00:11:25,140
and behave properly
within your jurisdiction

196
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:27,760
instead of swaggering around here.

197
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:31,200
