204
00:11:49,820 --> 00:11:51,906
Arase, I'm fine.

205
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:56,190
Arase.

206
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:00,794
I told you that I am fine.

207
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,420
Folks,

208
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:11,060
