of bullying the weak, alright?

209
00:12:14,020 --> 00:12:15,740
Arase, don't forget that

210
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:18,880
you have previously conducted
an illegal undercover search.

211
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:21,300
You should be well aware of the
consequences if any trouble arises again.

212
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:24,020
We have the ability to fabricate charges
against you out of thin air if we wish.

213
00:12:24,020 --> 00:12:27,780
