216
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:37,220
Mr. Iwa, I did not expect you to be
slacking around and picking fights.

217
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:39,240
Oh dear, be careful.

218
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:40,795
Are you okay?

219
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:49,280
