00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:55,083
The Solitaire video incident
has caused police unrest.

244
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:57,380
You mean that there is a traitor, right?

245
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,247
Yes, the higher-ups

246
00:13:59,247 --> 00:14:03,126
seemed to believe that the sniper incident
was orchestrated by Solitaire himself.

247
00:14:03,560 --> 00:14:06,420
But it's better for you to avoid trouble
as much as possible.

248
00:14:06,880 --> 00:14:10,049
Even in my position,
I have limited ability to protect you.

249
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:12,900
I am grateful

250
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,701
even if you can only provide me
with limited protection.

251
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:17,432
I'll take my leave then.

252
00:14:19,700 --> 00:14:20,910
You need to be more careful.

253
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:26,160
Although it's currently
just my speculation,

254
00:14:26,274 --> 00:14:28,180
this matter may be related to

255
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:31,420
the Lemmings and other calamities.

256
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:33,506
That's truly frightening.

257
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:36,785
So, the more trustworthy people
we have, the better.

258
00:14:36,785 --> 00:14:38,820
-Old man.
-Well.

259
00:14:39,260 --> 00:14:42,180
I was actually going to tell you

260
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:44,084
not to deepen the conflict between
you and headquarters.

261
00:14:44,520 --> 00:14:48,300
I think that person simply dislikes you.

262
00:14:48,540 --> 00:14:49,874
Whatever, Yatsu.

263
00:14:50,620 --> 00:14:54,220
However, our Comps-3 mission
remains unchanged,

264
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:57,510
which is to wholeheartedly
protect the city's safety.

265
00:14:58,300 --> 00:14:59,593
We have to fight against

266
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:03,300
those crazy calamities until the end.

267
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:11,180
I can't believe even the Lei family's
intelligence network

268
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,191
couldn't find the whereabouts of Hosorogi.

269
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,560
Footsteps on the roof?

270
00:15:17,380 --> 00:15:19,452
Oh, every time I land from the roof,

271
00:15:19,452 --> 00:15:22,247
I feel incredibly excited.

272
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:25,320
This excitement stems from
the guilt of committing a crime

273
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:26,560
or

274
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:30,255
the tension of potential enemies
lurking ahead.

275
00:15:30,547 --> 00:15:33,020
No, no, not at all!

276
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:35,300
It is a kind of intoxication.

277
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:37,040
Since the copyright to the works

278
00:15:37,137 --> 00:15:40,660
of the great writer Edogawa Ranpo
has also expired,

279
00:15:40,849 --> 00:15:44,060
I suppose I can even call myself
"The Fiend with Twenty Faces"

280
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:45,854
without causing offense.

281
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:48,300
Hold on a moment.

282
00:15:48,523 --> 00:15:51,104
This could be considered offensive
to fans of Ranpo, right?

283
00:15:51,104 --> 00:15:52,288
AND IT SEEMED QUITE OFFENSIVE…

284
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,325
What do you think?

285
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:59,760
I didn't expect such a warm welcome
right from the start.

286
00:16:00,201 --> 00:16:02,880
It seems my intuition is correct.

287
00:16:03,260 --> 00:16:05,480
So, can you please tell me

288
00:16:05,707 --> 00:16:08,400
have you been affiliated with
any particular organization?

289
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:11,015
And tell me about that sign!

290
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:13,360
Corpse God diviner.

291
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:16,400
No, I should call you Polka Shinoyama!

292
00:16:18,344 --> 00:16:21,560
Please do not compare me to that weak guy.

293
00:16:23,780 --> 00:16:24,780
Who are you?

294
00:16:25,408 --> 00:16:26,080
AT THAT TIME, POLKA

295
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:46,449
Bamboo cage, bamboo cage.

296
00:16:46,980 --> 00:16:51,320
Oh, little bird in the cage,

297
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:55,893
when will you come out?

298
00:16:56,420 --> 00:17:00,424
On the eve of dawn,

299
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:05,249
both the crane and the turtle slipped.

300
00:17:05,840 --> 00:17:09,854
Who is the person behind me?

301
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:12,500
Hurry up! The army has been
devoured by the sinkhole.

302
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:13,900
Where is General Daryl?

303
00:17:14,120 --> 00:17:16,580
Their entire force has been taken away
by the Lewd and Cruel Dragon!

304
00:17:16,740 --> 00:17:19,576
Did they escape? That's why I said
not to trust the Dragon Clan.

305
00:17:19,900 --> 00:17:23,540
-What about the Prince and the Queen?
-What are you doing, foolish apprentice?

306
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,369
There are barriers around us
that hinder understanding.

307
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:30,799
Otherwise, we would definitely be involved
and sent to the front line.

308
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,127
You ask why I don't go?

309
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:37,180
I simply don't want to destroy myself
with that bunch of foolish people.

310
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:42,237
I've asked Romelka to help as many people
as possible that we know well.

311
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:48,582
What Utsurojuza said is right.
It's time to stop.

312
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:51,029
You should also get ready.

313
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:53,980
You ask what I get ready for?

314
00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:56,653
Get ready to break free from
the shackles of the Empire

315
00:17:56,943 --> 00:17:59,195
and live a free life from now on.

316
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:01,751
I have already made you

317
00:18:02,040 --> 00:18:04,840
possess the bones of an elderly person,

318
00:18:05,243 --> 00:18:08,100
but your mentality still
resembles that of a child.

319
00:18:09,040 --> 00:18:10,041
Forget it.

320
00:18:10,580 --> 00:18:13,291
You will gradually mature in the future.

321
00:18:14,840 --> 00:18:17,384
We have unlimited time.

322
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,284
However, in contrast,

323
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:22,020
we should try our best to cherish

324
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:24,732
those who live within
a limited time frame.

325
00:18:26,420 --> 00:18:28,260
I'm sorry.

326
00:18:28,700 --> 00:18:29,951
I'm sorry, Master.

327
00:18:31,853 --> 00:18:33,700
I failed to act according
to your instructions.

328
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:36,258
I failed to protect them,

329
00:18:37,066 --> 00:18:38,526
failed to save them,

330
00:18:39,520 --> 00:18:41,605
and failed to let go of this matter.

331
00:18:42,580 --> 00:18:45,416
I have tarnished the abilities
you imparted to me.

332
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:48,680
I am ashamed to face
the people of the Empire.

333
00:18:49,820 --> 00:18:52,698
I have become the enemy of the world.

334
00:18:54,800 --> 00:18:57,762
I have escaped from my own world.

335
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:04,440
I no longer have the ability
to cherish anything.

336
00:19:05,300 --> 00:19:07,261
You are still so foolish,

337
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:08,851
my dear friend.

338
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,680
Your Majesty.

339
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:18,300
Alright, alright, I have already awakened.

340
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,640
It seems like there's a smell
of something burnt.

341
00:19:30,787 --> 00:19:31,871
What is it?

342
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:35,680
Are you still afraid of ghosts?

343
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:39,557
No, if it's the work of a ghost,
I can sense it.

344
00:19:41,320 --> 00:19:42,613
It's still warm.

345
00:19:50,220 --> 00:19:51,320
Hello there.

346
00:19:51,540 --> 00:19:54,966
Are you Polka Shinoyama?

347
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,892
Who are you?

348
00:19:59,315 --> 00:20:00,240
Hello?

349
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:02,561
Are you…

350
00:20:03,820 --> 00:20:06,907
a product of Sabaramond as well?

351
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:13,995
Why? Why do you know this name?

352
00:20:17,220 --> 00:20:19,431
So that's how it is.

353
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:22,600
They're really malicious,

354
00:20:22,900 --> 00:20:26,445
dragging me into this destined prank.

355
00:20:27,040 --> 00:20:29,459
"They"? Who are you referring to?

356
00:20:30,179 --> 00:20:33,660
I recall this guy is the wanted criminal
everyone is talking about right now.

357
00:20:34,300 --> 00:20:35,563
He didn't even react!

358
00:20:35,893 --> 00:20:37,600
Who exactly is this child?

359
00:20:37,728 --> 00:20:40,880
Despite my mysterious speech,
I do not know what to do next.

360
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:42,360
I need to calm down and think.

361
00:20:42,860 --> 00:20:44,153
Forget it.

362
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:45,806
Once I catch you,

363
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:49,040
I'll slowly interrogate you.

364
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:53,002
Don't be in such a hurry, young man.

365
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:54,940
You're still young.

366
00:20:55,180 --> 00:20:57,420
It's already 3 a.m.,

367
00:20:57,623 --> 00:20:59,480
and the child should go back to sleep.

368
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:02,011
I'm already nineteen years old.

369
00:21:05,089 --> 00:21:06,200
So fast!

370
00:21:06,880 --> 00:21:08,966
Indeed, this is definitely not something
a child could be capable of,

371
00:21:09,552 --> 00:21:11,580
but it's not at a level
where it's unavoidable.

372
00:21:19,145 --> 00:21:20,771
Huh?

373
00:21:32,575 --> 00:21:33,743
Has he started to act?

374
00:21:34,620 --> 00:21:38,140
However, it is slightly different
from what we expected.

375
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:41,592
I didn't expect that the joyful offender

376
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:45,540
would actually fight with
my grandpa's personal bodyguard.

377
00:21:47,715 --> 00:21:49,217
Let's start taking action as well.

378
00:21:51,820 --> 00:21:52,880
How can we reap the benefits

379
00:21:53,360 --> 00:21:55,571
in the midst of a melee?

380
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:59,240
This often plays a crucial role

381
00:22:00,220 --> 00:22:02,806
in controlling chaotic situations.

382
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:40,063
(Episode 12: The Sacred Place)

